&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Utilize a variety of instructional strategies and technologies to enhance learning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
